HEADWORD: Guardsman
<hw>Guards"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Guardsmen</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
guards; a guard.</def>⟦br⟧
